data.description:
Your own Florida dream residence awaits. Located in the highly sought-after community of Palm Meadows Estates, this 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom pool home is replete with luxurious features and modern upgrades. As you arrive you will be greeted by a professionally landscaped yard from the front of the house to the tropical oasis that is your backyard. A custom impact glass door leads to the foyer which features high ceilings and an exquisite chandelier.The main floor of the residence boasts a formal dining room, a great room, and an upgraded kitchen with a gas stove and high end venting. Other features on the main floor are 24x24 polished porcelain tile floors and custom window treatments including modern plantation shutters and motorized fabric verticals. Once you step through the impact sliding glass doors you will enter a screened patio which is your gateway to tropical paradise. The marble pool deck features an opulent heated pool and spa overlooking the lake. The pool is salt chlorinated and contains 20 different LEDs which, when illuminated, create a breathtaking view. The laminar spa with jets and bubbles is perfect for relaxation. A summer kitchen includes hook ups for gas, water and electric. The pristine landscaping extends all the way around the fenced backyard creating a lush and private ambiance. Coupled with the gas fireplace and beautiful lake views this is the perfect place location for serene contemplation or outdoor entertaining.

After a long day enjoying the South Florida lifestyle you will retire to the second floor which features laminate hardwood floors throughout. The primary suite is your own private retreat with a spa-like en-suite bathroom and custom walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms are of good size and provide ample space for family and guests, or versatility to use an office. All the bedrooms have custom California style closets and upgraded window treatments.

When it comes to amenities Palm Meadows Estates is truly exceptional. Enjoy the community pool, a fitness center, an indoor basketball court, and pickleball and tennis courts. Everything is at your fingertips for living an active lifestyle and entertaining friends and family. Located in a prime location in Boynton Beach, there is easy access to plethora of restaurants, retail shopping, and attractions. All the schools that link to this community are A rated. Close to transportation via 95 or the turnpike means everything is just moments away.

This property truly has it all. Luxury lifestyle, elegant and modern upgrades, and exceptional amenities and location. Book your showing today and welcome to your new Florida dream home.
